*Bag Policy::   All approved bags are subject to inspection upon entry and are subject to additional inspections within AT&T Stadium. AT&T Stadium has modified its security policy by limiting the size and style of bags allowed in the stadium.  Visit www.attstadium.com/bags for more information.
